assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Tijara & Real Estate Investment Company K.S.C.P., together with its subsidiaries, purchases, sells, and exchanges land and real estate properties in Kuwait and internationally. It operates through two segments, Real Estate Management and Investment Management. The company is involved in the construction and development of buildings, and leasing and rental of commercial and residential complexes. It also manages real estate properties, as well as purchases and sells securities of companies. In addition, the company undertakes maintenance works of buildings and real estate properties, such as civil, mechanical, and air-conditioning works. Further, it invests in equities and other investments. The company was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Kuwait City, Kuwait.
